<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #1976d2;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .success-box {
      background-color: #e8f5e9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .rating-box {
      background-color: #fff3e0;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #1976d2;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Order Completed Successfully!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi {{username}},</p>
      
      <div class="success-box">
        <h2>ðŸŽ‰ Thank You!</h2>
        <p>Your order has been marked as completed.</p>
      </div>

      <p><strong>Order Details:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Product: {{productUrl}}</li>
        <li>Order ID: {{orderId}}</li>
        <li>Total Amount: IDR {{amount}}</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="rating-box">
        <h3>Rate Your Experience</h3>
        <p>Help us improve by rating your experience with the traveler.</p>
        <p>
          <a href="{{ratingUrl}}" class="button">Rate Now</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>We hope you enjoyed using our service! If you need to purchase anything else from overseas, feel free to create another request.</p>

      <p>
        <a href="{{createNewUrl}}" class="button">Create New Request</a>
      </p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>Team Bagasi</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
      <p>Â© {{year}} Bagasi. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
